dcterms:description: A dataset containing 0.5 million unlabeled small images randomly cropped from 400 lung adenocarcinoma histopathology images obtained from the public TCGA repository.
dcterms:title: Dataset for Unsupervised Learning

dcterms:description: A dataset of 23,356 images labeled as lymphocyte (including plasma cells) rich or not, cropped from lung adenocarcinoma tissue images in the publicly available TCGA dataset.
dcterms:title: Dataset for Lymphocyte Classification Experiments

dcterms:description: A dataset of 1785 images of individual objects labeled lymphocyte or non-lymphocyte by a pathologist, cropped from 12 representative lung adenocarcinoma whole slide tissue images from the TCGA repository.
dcterms:title: Dataset for Classifying Individual Lymphocytes Experiments

dcterms:creator: V. Murthy
L. Hou
D. Samaras
T. M. Kurc
J. H. Saltz
dcterms:description: A dataset consisting of 2000 images of nuclei labeled with fifteen morphology attributes and shapes for nuclear shape and attribute classification.
dcterms:title: Dataset for Nuclear Shape and Attribute Classification Experiments

dcterms:description: A dataset from the MICCAI 2015 nucleus segmentation challenge containing 15 training images and 18 testing images with ground truth masks of nuclei.
dcterms:title: Dataset for Nucleus Segmentation Experiments
